	(7,'About 2 Slide 1','about-2-slide-1',NULL,NULL,'<p style=\"text-align: center;\">[row padding_top=\"\" padding_bottom=\"\" bg=\"\" bg_light=\"true\" appear=\"false\"] [column size=\"1-1\" appear=\"false\"]</p>\n\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">?Sleek? -Beautifully Crafted For Bloggers</h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #3f3f53;\">[separator size=\"medium\" center=\"true\" empty=\"false\" opaque=\"true\" margin_top=\"\" margin_bottom=\"\"]</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #ffffff; font-size: 20px;\">During these days of preparation, Queequeg and I often visited the craft, and as often I asked about Captain Ahab, and when he was going to come on board his ship. To these questions they would answer, that he was getting better and better, was expected aboard every day meantime the two captains could attend to everything.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">[button url=\"#\" new_tab=\"false\" size=\"medium\" style=\"outline\" color=\"false\" light=\"false\"]Learn More[/button][button url=\"#\" new_tab=\"false\" size=\"medium\" style=\"solid\" color=\"true\" light=\"false\"]Choose Sleek[/button]</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">[/column] [/row]</p>',NULL,NULL,9,'2014-10-11 18:36:08','2014-10-11 18:36:08',1,'http://sleek.korra.io/?post_type=sleek-slider&#038;p=3187',1,1,1,1,0,NULL,NULL),
	(8,'About 2 Slide 2','about-2-slide-2',NULL,NULL,'<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">Fluid &amp; Responsive Layout</h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">[separator size=\"medium\" center=\"true\" empty=\"false\" opaque=\"true\" margin_top=\"\" margin_bottom=\"\"]</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px; color: #ffffff;\">At last, stepping on board the Pequod, we found everything in profound quiet.</span>\n<span style=\"font-size: 20px; color: #ffffff;\"> The cabin entrance was locked within; the hatches were all on, and lumbered with coils of rigging.</span>\n<span style=\"font-size: 20px; color: #ffffff;\"> Going forward to the forecastle, we found the slide of the scuttle open.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">[button url=\"#\" new_tab=\"false\" size=\"medium\" style=\"outline\" color=\"false\" light=\"false\"]Learn More[/button] [button url=\"#\" new_tab=\"false\" size=\"medium\" style=\"solid\" color=\"true\" light=\"false\"]Choose Sleek[/button]</p>',NULL,NULL,9,'2014-10-11 18:37:52','2014-10-11 18:37:52',1,'http://sleek.korra.io/?post_type=sleek-slider&#038;p=3189',1,1,1,1,0,NULL,NULL),
