	(147,'10 Benefits of becoming a accountant','4446-revision-v1',NULL,NULL,'There are many rewarding factors of pursuing a career in accounting. For starters a high salary is a big bonus and there is always room to progress. Accountants also receive the following:\n\n<strong>Job security</strong>\n\nAccountants are very important and are a crucial part of running a business. After their studies they are very likely to find a job in their chosen career.\n\n<strong>A clear future</strong>\n\nIf you?re looking for a clear career path with no surprises, accounting may be the perfect choice; your education will provide you with sought-after skills that almost every business needs. The Bureau of Labor Statistics foresees a growth of 13% in accounting and auditing jobs through 2020. It?s definitely not a bad time to be an accountant!\n\n<strong>High salary</strong>\n\nThe average wage of an accountant is 25,000. When you have learnt your trade you can see figures rising to 50,000+. Results show that female accountants are considered having one of the top ten highest salaries.\n\n<strong>Benefits</strong>\n\nThere are many full-time accounting positions that offer benefits. Some of these include: health care, pensions and sometimes the opportunity to become a partner in the business.\n\n<strong>Opportunity for advancement</strong>\n\nSenior accountants may eventually double the wage of an entry level accountant. Accountants are always in demand, so it would be fairly easy to change to work in a different location.\n\n<strong>A great network</strong>\n\nWhen working as an accountant you will develop contacts that can help you learn and improve your skills. You can also refer to these contacts for advice if needed.\n\n<strong>Career diversity</strong>\n\nThere are many different careers that someone who has studied accounting can go in to. Some of these include careers in: finance, auditing, taxation, accounting, business and many more. You can study in a number of sectors for example: a small firm or corporation, the government, the private sector, or you may even start your own company. When learning about finances it will put you in a great position to manage any account.\n\n<strong>Developed Technology</strong>\n\nWith new software and technology, it will make your job a lot easier. It will also point out finer aspects, which will help make more accurate financial decision-making.\n\n<strong>A rewarding role</strong>\n\nAccountants will have strong relationships with their clients and will act as their advisors. Accountants have the chance to make a true difference to a company. Although they work with numbers, this affects everyone.\n\n<strong>Gain skills on the job</strong>\n\nAn accounting role will provide you with useful skills, as well as responsibilities. Business owners will place great trust in you and will respect the core values of your career.',NULL,NULL,9,'2016-01-04 16:18:35','2016-01-04 16:18:35',1,'http://blog.openstudycollege.com/2016/01/04/4446-revision-v1/',1,1,1,0,0,NULL,NULL),
	(148,'Fancy yourself as the next winner of The Great British Bake-off? Study our cake making course','4344-autosave-v1',NULL,NULL,'Is there a celebration coming up? Maybe a birthday or christening? Then now is the time to develop your cake making skills and show them off. Our course will help you do just that from home. Here\'s 4 reasons why you should study cake making:\n\n<h2>Wide audience </h2>\n\nThis course will inspire anyone with an interest in baking, to those people that know nothing about making cakes and want to learn. You never know you could surprise someone or maybe appear on the next Great British Bake-off!\n\n<h2>Fun while studying</h2>\n\nAs you will be studying about different types of cakes, why not have a go at creating them. Making more, means eating more! It would be rude to let them go to waste. This will also help putting what you have learnt into practice. Improvements can also be made from family and friends. That?s if you want to share anyway!\n\n<h2>Interesting</h2>\n\nHave you ever wondered how wedding cakes look so amazing? How they have managed to decorate them with flowers and petals? Well you will have an insight in sugar craft and decoration with this course. You will learn all of the different techniques and knowledge in order to create your own designs, however wacky they are.\n\n<strong>Study from home</strong>\n\nAs we are a distance learning college, this will allow you to study from home. You don?t need to put your efforts into getting up in the morning and commuting to a cold classroom. You can also receive tutor support by email, so help is only a click away!\n\nGet your apron on and <a href=\"https://www.openstudycollege.com/courses/cake-making-2.html\">study cake making</a> today!\n\n<a class=\"blog-cta\" href=\"https://www.openstudycollege.com/courses/cake-making-2.html\">Cake Making Level 2</a>',NULL,NULL,9,'2017-03-29 12:01:59','2017-03-29 12:01:59',1,'http://blog.openstudycollege.com/2016/01/04/4344-autosave-v1/',1,1,