man planes were destroyed.\n\nDo you want to know more about the Battle of Britain? Then enrol on our World War 2 Course today!\n\nTake a look at our World War 2 Level 3 Course&gt;&gt;',NULL,NULL,9,'2016-03-21 15:34:42','2016-03-21 15:34:42',1,'https://blog.openstudycollege.com/2016/03/21/4949-revision-v1/',1,1,1,0,0,NULL,NULL),
