	(497,'4 Tips on choosing the perfect course','4-tips-on-choosing-the-perfect-course',NULL,NULL,'Choosing the right course can be very difficult for some of us and that?s why you need to take into consideration these 4 very important tips to help you pick the perfect one:\n<h2>Why do you want to study a new course?</h2>\nThe most important factor when choosing your course is why you are looking to study. Maybe you want to move up the career ladder? If this is the case then you should be looking in a topic area that is relevant to your current workplace. You should discuss with you manager or colleagues what the best qualification would be to help you achieve this. Perhaps you want to diversify your knowledge or change career path completely? Then think about what you enjoy learning about and what area you would like to work in ever day.\n<h2>What are you interested in?</h2>\nThink about what you are really interested in. By questioning yourself now can help you work out the exact path you want your course to take you on. Don?t take any notice of what other people want you to do, it is YOUR decision.\n<h2>How do you like to study?</h2>\nDo you like to study online or are you better learning out of a course pack? You need to take into consideration how you study the best. Do youlike the idea of having all your course materials online and being able to study on a computer? Or maybe you like to write, highlight and underline informationin your course pack? With over half of our courses offering both online and course pack you have a wide range to choose from!\n<h2>Talk to a student adviser</h2>\nIf you are still struggling to find yourperfect course contact our friendly student advisers and they will be able to answer any questions you may have. Give them a call on 08009709131 or <a href=\"https://www.openstudycollege.com/contact_us.php\">contact us</a>.\n\n<a href=\"https://www.openstudycollege.com/contact_us.php\">Contact us now!</a>',NULL,NULL,9,'2016-08-24 12:44:41'