	(523,'3 Reasons why it?s never too late to change your career','3-reasons-why-its-never-too-late-to-change-your-career',NULL,NULL,'It is never too late to change your career however old you are. It can have many benefits from a higher salary, new ways of working and gaining new knowledge. Here are 3 reasons why it?s never too late to change your career:\n<h2>New goals and ambitions</h2>\nAs we get older and our knowledge develops, we start to want new things. Your interests, desires and dreams change from the first time since you entered the workplace. Maybe you would love to set up your own business? Or become a manager in another organisation? If you truly believe in something you should go for it!\n<h2>No longer interested in what you do</h2>\nIf you are losing interest in your job it is never too late to change your career. If it is too challenging for you to stay engaged then you definitely need to consider leaving. We spend most of our time at work so doing something that makes you happy is vital. Don?t spend your working life wishing you had gone down a different route, do something about it now!\n<h2>Not getting anywhere in your current career</h2>\nIf your current job no longer challenges you should take the opportunity to leave and gain a higher position elsewhere. Finding a job that keeps you on your toes and presents you with a new challenge every day will help you progress whilst developing your skills.\n\nA qualification can be the difference in achieving your perfect job.\n\nStudy a course with us today and take the first steps in your journey to a new career!\n\n<a href=\"https://www.openstudycollege.com/contact_us.php\">Contact us to know more about our courses&gt;&gt;</a>',NULL,NULL,9,'2016-08-16 11:32:07','2016-08-16 11:32:07',2,'https://blog.openstudycollege.com/?p=5738',1,1,1,0,0,NULL,NULL),
