	(602,'3 Reasons why you should study sociology','3-reasons-study-sociology',NULL,NULL,'Are you interested in human behaviour? Do you want to explore the patterns of society? Then a Sociology course is perfect for you! Here are 3 reasons why you should study Sociology:\n<h2>Interesting subject</h2>\nBy studying one of our sociology courses, you will gain a fascinating insight into various topics from exploring different types of families to looking at crime and social deviance. You will be able to learn about different types of methodology including primary and secondary data, qualitative and quantitative data and the strengths and weaknesses of them. You?ll struggle to put your course down!\n<h2>Understand your own culture and identity</h2>\nStudying sociology will allow you to make sense of society in terms of your own culture and identify. Learning about types of families and social classes and values will enable you to understand your own life.\n<h2>Opens up a wide range of opportunities</h2>\nA sociology course will help kick-start your future prospects and open up a wide range of careers. So if you want to become an advice worker, community development worker, family support worker or social researcher then why not begin your journey and boost your knowledge with a flexible home learning course!\n\nEnrol on one of our <a href=\"https://www.openstudycollege.com/sociology_courses.html\">Sociology courses</a> today!\n\n<a href=\"https://www.openstudycollege.com/sociology_courses.html\">Take a look at our Sociology courses&gt;&gt;</a>',NULL,NULL,9,'2016-10-20 12:46:55','2017-03-31 11:35:01',2,'https://blog.openstudycollege.com/?p=5947',1,1,1,0,0,NULL,NULL),
