	(643,'3 Reasons why you should study biology','3-reasons-study-biology',NULL,NULL,'Do you find biology fascinating and want to know more? Maybe you?d love to gain the knowledge to begin your journey to pursue a career in this field as a biologist or even a Pharmacologist? Then here are 3 reasons why you should study biology:\n<h2>Fascinating Information</h2>\nBiology allows us to explore the natural world around us. It can help find out information about the physical structure of our bodies, which can then help us to produce cures and treatments for many diseases. It can also let us focus on plants, including their different parts and how they support us. It is very important that we understand why humans and animals behave the way they do and know the different functions that keep us alive.\n<h2>Range of opportunities</h2>\nWhen you study biology you can progress into a wide range of careers, especially in healthcare, medicine and jobs involving plants or animals. Some of the jobs you can go into include: nursing, dentistry, forensic science, psychology and many more!\n<h2>Explore the world</h2>\nIs it your dream to explore the world? Then imagine doing just that for your job! Asbiologists deal with the natural world, their job can take them literally anywhere! From labs to zoos to ocean liners in the arctic and fieldwork in the Amazon jungle, the possibilities are endless.\n\nEnrol on our <a href=\"https://www.openstudycollege.com/courses/biology-3.html\">Biology Level 3 course</a> today!\n\n<a class=\"blog-cta\" href=\"https://www.openstudycollege.com/courses/biology-3.html\">Take a look at our Biology Level 3 course</a>',NULL,NULL,9,'2016-11-09 10:57:13','2017-03-31 12:07:04',2,'https://blog.openstudycollege.com/?p=6044',1,1,1,0,0,NULL,NULL),
