	(678,'3 Reasons why you should study our exotic animal care course','study-exotic-animal-care-course',NULL,NULL,'Do you want to boost your knowledgeof how to care for some of the most fascinating animals? Maybe you have a passion for animals and dream of a career as a zookeeper orveterinarian? Then our Exotic Animal Care Level 3 course is perfect for you! Here are 3 reasons why you should enrol on our Exotic Animal Care course:\n<h2>Interesting subject</h2>\nBy studying our Exotic Animal Care Level 3 course, you will gain a fascinating insight into various topics from the history of exotic pets to looking at the concerns with conservation. You will be able to explore different types of animals from chipmunks, ferrets, turtles, lizards, snakes, aviary birds and many more. You?ll struggle to put this course down!\n<h2>Put your theory into practice</h2>\nIf you have a pet lizard, chinchilla, tortoise or any other exotic animal, you will be able to put what you have learnt into practice. Understand how to care for them in terms of their nutrition, anatomy and common diseases.\n<h2>Opens up a wide range of opportunities</h2>\nThis course will help kick-start your future prospects and open up a wide range of careers. So if you want to become an animal trainer, veterinarian or zookeeper then why not begin your journey and boost your knowledge with our Level 3 course!\n\nEnrol on our <a href=\"https://www.openstudycollege.com/courses/exotic-animal-care.html\">Exotic Animal Care</a>course now!\n\n<a href=\"https://www.openstudycollege.com/courses/exotic-animal-care.html\">Take a look at our Exotic Animal Care Level 3 course&gt;&gt;</a>',NULL,NULL,9,'2016-10-21 09:24:46','2017-03-31 11:38:08',2,'https://blog.openstudycollege.com/?p=6105',1,1,1,0,0,NULL,NULL),
