	(1004,'How a brand identity failure cost a business more than 50 million dollars','5369-autosave-v1',NULL,NULL,'Brand identity plays a major part in the success of a business. It can either make or break a company and in this case it turned out to be a disaster for one of the leading fruit juice companies, Tropicana. Here\'s how theirbrand identity failure\n\nThey invested 35 million dollars into creating new packaging and advertising campaigns - which was the biggest mistake they could have made! This was launched in January 2009 and was first used on their best-selling product: Tropicana Pure Premium, which makes them more than 700 million dollars per year in North America.\n\nThe packaging was soon criticised as being ?ugly? and ?cheap? and people took to social media to make sure the company knew about it. As Tropicana is perceived as a premium brand, consumers were confused as to why they would create a ?low-range supermarket looking? brand.\n\nBecause of this, their sales dropped by 20% which resulted into a huge loss of 30 million dollars for Tropicana. When the disaster couldn\'t get any worse, competitors took advantage of the Tropicana crisis and gained most of their sales.\n\nIn February 2009 theyannounced that they would return to its original packaging and within a few months it was back on our shelves. In total this brand identity failure cost Tropicana a whopping 50 million dollars!\n\nWhat Tropicana forgot is that their consumers feel an emotional bond with the appearance of their products. By changing the designs so much peoplecould no longer identify the brand with the product ? this is a vital factor to focus on before making changes to packaging. Tropicana?s main problem was that they changed too many of their brand elements, which confused their customers and had a negative effect on sales.\n\nI\'m sure this is a failure that Tropicana wants to forget!\n\n<a href=\"https://www.openstudycollege.com/courses/introduction-marketing-3.html\">Learn how you can create a successful brand identity on our Introduction to Marketing Level 3 course&gt;&gt;</a>',NULL,NULL,9,'2017-03-30 13:28:25','2017-03-30 13:28:25',1,'https://blog.openstudycollege.com/5369-autosave-v1/',1,1,1,0,0,NULL,NULL),
	(1005,'Boost your skills with an acrylic nails diploma','5760-autosave-v1',NULL,NULL,'Do you dream of becoming an acrylic nail technician? Maybe you want to set up your own salon? Well our acrylic nail diploma course can help you do just that! Here are 3 reasons why you gain an acrylic nails diploma:\n<h2>Improve your knowledge</h2>\nThis course will allow you to learn everything you need to know about acrylic nails from applying the acrylic to shaping and finishing. You will also gain an insight into how to become a nail technician and learn how to manage a salon environment. This will help if you want to open your own salon in the future.\n<h2>Added extras</h2>\nWe will provide you with lots of free added extras to help you complete the course. You will receive a free 2 hour teaching DVD where renowned nail expert Gina Wallace demonstrates professional techniques to help you become trained in acrylic nails. Along with this we will also provide you with a free nail trainer practice hand. This will enable you to create your nail extensions and help simulate the experience of providing a service to clients in a salon. You will also receive a free Essential Nail kit which will include a whole range of professional equipment from cetuem polish to cuticle oil. So you can start learning as soon as you receive your course!\n<h2>Gain insurance</h2>\nIf your dream is to work as a professional nail technician then this course is perfect for you. By successfully completing this course you will be awarded a Certification by The Essential Nail Institute, which is nationally recognised within the nail industry. You will also be able to gain your professional indemnity insurance with this certificate. This means you will be covered to work from home, mobile or in a salon and you will be fully recognised by HABIA, the British Learning Association, Guild of Professional Beauty Therapists and Professional Beauty Direct.\n\nEnrol on our <a href=\"https://www.openstudycollege.com/courses/acrylic-nails-course.html?dc=11\">Professional Acrylic Nails Diploma course</a> today!\n\n<a href=\"https://www.openstudycollege.com/courses/acrylic-nails-course.html?dc=11\">Take a look at our Professional Acrylic Nails Diploma course&gt;&gt;</a>',NULL,NULL,9,'2017-03-30 15:46:24','2017-03-30 15:46:24',1,'https://blog.openstudycollege.com/5760-autosave-v1/',1,1,1,0,0,NULL,NULL);
