	(1061,'Is a career as an Event Manager for me?','career-event-manager',NULL,NULL,'Being an Event Managercan be stressful, but very exciting and rewarding at the same time. Do you find yourself asking the same question over and over again - is a career as an Event Manager for me? If so, read on...\n<h2>What is an Event Manager?</h2>\nFor every event you have ever been to there was an Event Manager behind it.Theyplan every tiny aspect of an event to make sure it runs smoothlyand on budget, keeping both their clients and attendees happy. Organisational skills and creativity are a must if you are going to succeed in the events industry. If you decide a career in Event Management is for you, then yourcareer will be filled with variety and excitement.\n<h2><strong>Why is being an Event Manager so great?</strong></h2>\n<h3><strong>Money, money, money</strong></h3>\nThe kind of salary you can expect throughout your career as an Event Manager ranges from the following:\n<ul>\n 	<li>17,000 - 21,000 when you first start</li>\n 	<li>25,000 - 40,000 for an experienced position</li>\n 	<li>50,000+ for a highly-experienced Event Manager</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>Variety is the spice of life</strong></h3>\nNo two days are the same in the events industry as clients, budgets and event briefs vary from event to event. There are also plenty ofopportunities to travel as it\'s likely you will be responsible for organising events abroad too!\n<h3><strong>I did that?</strong></h3>\nWhen you have poured all of your time, creativity and passion into an event and you see it all come together, your clients are happy, and the attendees enjoyed themselves, the greatsense of pride and achievement you feel makes all those months of hard work worth it.\n\nAn Event Management course can provide you with the skill set and fundamental knowledge you need to kick-start your career. Take a look at <a href=\"https://www.openstudycollege.com/\">our website</a> for information on the Event Management courses that we offer, or call a Student Adviser on 03300 563100.\n\n<a class=\"blog-cta\" href=\"https://www.openstudycollege.com/event-management_courses.html\">Enrol now</a>',NULL,NULL,9,'2017-05-19 09:00:51','2017-11-13 10:06:37',2,'https://blog.openstudycollege.com/?p=7057',1,1,1,0,0,NULL,NULL),
