ter and could further my career.?</em></h3>\n</blockquote>\nIf you would like to learn more about our AAT Accounting courses that we offer, and how they can help you, head over to our website.',NULL,NULL,9,'2017-06-22 10:43:45','2017-06-22 10:43:45',1,'https://blog.openstudycollege.com/7220-revision-v1/',1,1,1,0,0,NULL,NULL),
