	(1224,'How can our Wedding Photography course help your career?','wedding-photography-course-help-career',NULL,NULL,'Whether you are a complete novice, or you\'re a photographer with no wedding photography experience, our Wedding Photography course will help you get started. Maybe you are looking for a new hobby, or you want to change your career? It is important that you understand what makes wedding photography different, and how to successfully shoot a wedding. Remember, a couple?s wedding photographs are a lasting reminder of their special day, so they will want beautiful pictures. Becoming a wedding photographer can provide you with a great source of incomeand a lucrative career.\n<h2>So, how can our Wedding Photography course help you to get started as a wedding photographer?</h2>\nOur Wedding Photography course covers everything you need to know to kick-start your wedding photography business. Here?s an overview of everything you will learn during the course?\n<h3>Unit 1 - Preparing to be a wedding photographer</h3>\nYour first unit will help you to understand what kit you will need to work as a wedding photographer and succeed. Learn how to shoot in manual mode, and respond to any wedding situation and effectively capture the moment.\n<h3>Unit 2 - Navigating the wedding day</h3>\nStudythe usualrunning order of a wedding day from start to finish, and the key moments to capture. You will also learn how to create packages that will appeal to potential customers, and build up a bank of poses.\n<h3>Unit 3 - Getting creative</h3>\nLearn how to get creative with your wedding photography when taking shotsof couples and groups. This unit will also teach you how to organise people to achieve creative shots, particularly in unplanned weather conditions.\n<h3>Unit 4 ? Night time shooting</h3>\nStudy the issues associated with night time photographs, as well as how to successfully capture night shots of the happy couple and groups. With this unit, you will understand th