	(1361,'The simple way to become a mortgage adviser','6054-autosave-v1',NULL,NULL,'Do you want to become a mortgage adviser? To help achieve your dream career a qualification recognised by the Financial Conduct Authority (FCA) is needed, which is where an Open Study College CeMAP course can help you! Here are 3 reasons why you should study our CeMAP course:\n<h2>Become a qualified mortgage adviser</h2>\nA CeMAP course is perfect if you want to kick-start your mortgage advising career. It meets the standards set by the Financial Conduct Authority (FCA) and with 80% of mortgage advisers having achieved this certificate, it has been recognised as the leading qualification in the financial services industry. After studying the full qualification you will be awarded full certification and can add the designation ?CeMAP? after your name, confirming your qualification to potential employers and future clients!\n<h2>Understand the mortgage law</h2>\nThe course will help you gain in-depth knowledge into mortgage law. You find out how the law gives significant legal protection to borrowers against the enforcement of unfair bargains and how the house buying process works. You will also learn the stages from the first offer to a completion of a mortgage and the economic and regulatory factors for giving advice.\n<h2>Develop your knowledge of a mortgage adviser</h2>\nBoosting your knowledge of the role of a mortgage adviser will help you understand what is required when you go into the profession. You will explore how to advise on different types of mortgages, understand your client?s finances, provide information on repayments and mortgage protection and much more!\n\nKick-start your career and become a mortgage adviser with a <a href=\"https://www.openstudycollege.com/courses/cemap-mortage-adviser.html\">CeMAP qualification</a>!\n\n<a class=\"blog-cta\" href=\"https://www.openstudycollege.com/courses/cemap-mortage-adviser.html\">Take a look at our CeMAP course</a>',NULL,NULL,9