	(1401,'Online Courses - are they right for me?','online-courses-right',NULL,NULL,'We are in a world where we\'re constantly changing and adapting to the latest trends, so why should our learning be any different? For some, traditional classroom learning is the most beneficial to them. However, others are more prone to independent distance learning, which is where online courses come into play.\n\nThe internet plays a large role in most of our lives. We do our shopping, order food and even find love over the internet, so it makes sense that we now have the choice to study online.\n<h2><strong>How does it work?</strong></h2>\nOnline studying takes advantage of modern technology to simulate or enhance classic teaching methods. All the course content and information is provided online or via email, and the feedback and support is provided from a tutor throughout your complete journey.\n\nDifferent online courses have different specifications and are usually graded through assignments or final examinations.\n\nHere at Open Study College, we offer a range of courses from multiple awarding bodies to suit your career aspirations. Whether you are someone looking to improve their knowledge or gain vital qualifications, there is something to suit everyone.\n<h2><strong>How do I know if online courses are right for me?</strong></h2>\nDifferent people like to learn in different ways; what works for some may not work for others so it is necessary to understand what works for you in order to make the most of your learning.\n<ul>\n 	<li>Are you independent and want to take control of your own learning?</li>\n 	<li>Are you organised and able to manage your own time efficiently?</li>\n 	<li>Do you have a busy lifestyle and want your learning to fit around your schedule?</li>\n 	<li>Do you still want to be able to earn while you learn?</li>\n</ul>\nDoes this sound like you? Then online courses are definitely for you!\n\nBrowse our selection of courses,or give our team of expert Sales Advisers a call on <strong>03300 563100 </strong>to get enrolled on one of our online courses today!\n\n<a class=\"blog-cta\" href=\"https://www.openstudycollege.com/pages/how-it-works.html\">Take a look at our courses</a>',NULL,NULL,9,'2017-11-30 16:10:36','2017-11-30 16:10:36',2,'https://blog.openstudycollege.com/?p=7747',1,1,1,0,0,NULL,NULL),
