	(1483,'Equip yourself with the skills you need to succeed in 2018','4359-autosave-v1',NULL,NULL,'<strong>What?s your new year\'s resolution?</strong>\n\nIt\'s tough to stick to a resolution and if you\'re anything like me you\'ll have given up before you\'ve managed to pack up the Christmas decorations.\n\nBut it doesn\'t have to be like that.\n\nYou just need a little help to <strong>make sure that 2018 is <em>your</em> year</strong>.\n\nIf your resolution is to <strong>get a new job for the new year</strong> then you\'re up against fierce competition. In fact, in some cities there can be up to 50 people applying for each vacancy. So that\'s why you need something extra to stand out from the crowd.\n\nAdding extra skills can help you get the job you want. And you can study one of our courses from home in your spare time with full support from one of our expert tutors.\n\n<h2>Trusted independent awards to add value to your CV</h2>\n\nOur courses have been scrutinised and quality-assured by trusted educational institutions. And that\'s because it\'s easier to get a job when you have an employer recognised award on your CV.\n\nYou can choose from over 280 courses, from the comfort of your own home.\n\n<h2>Increase your chances of getting the job you want by studying from home at your own pace with full support from a tutor</h2>\n\n<strong>As over 50,000 people have found out</strong>, learning from home with Open Study College offers you a convenient way to improve your skills without interfering with your busy lifestyle.\n\nYou can study when you want at your own pace and enjoy full support by email from a helpful tutor.\n\n<ul>\n	<li>No strict deadlines</li>\n	<li>No timetables</li>\n	<li>No classes to attend</li>\n</ul>\n...It is the most flexible way of studying.\n\n<h2>We\'ll help you to create the perfect CV</h2>\n\n<strong>Do you want a CV that gets results?</strong>\n\nOur recruitment consultant can help. And when you\'ve successfully completed your studies she will work with you to create a CV that demands attention and gets your foot in the door for the job you really want.\n\nExtra skills and a professionally crafted CV to help you to get the job you want, it\'s just what you need for a successful 2018.\n\n<h2>Start studying with the UK\'s fastest growing distance learning college</h2>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Over 50,000 people have improved their skills with us</li>\n	<li>Trusted awards including A-Levels and iGCSEs</li>\n	<li>Study from home, at your own pace</li>\n	<li>Full support from an expert tutor</li>\n	<li>Accredited by the British Institute For Learning &amp; Development</li>\n	<li>Accredited by Open and Distance Learning Quality Council</li>\n	<li>Winners of Tutor of the Year and Small Training Provider of the Year at the Institute of Certified Bookkeepers Awards 2014</li>\n	<li>FREE NUS Extra Card</li>\n	<li>FREE CV writing service by our Recruitment Consultant</li>\n</ul>\n\nAre you ready to kick-start your career and make this year, your year?\n\n<a href=\"https://www.openstudycollege.com/contact_us.php\">Call us on 03300 563 100 or contact us here</a>',NULL,NULL,9,'2018-01-03 09:40:08','2018-01-03 09:40:08',1,'https://blog.openstudycollege.com/4359-autosave-v1/',1,1,1,0,0,NULL,NULL),
	(1484,'Reasons to Enrol with an Online College in 2018','enrol-online-college',NULL,NULL,'The future lies within online education.\n\nIn this day and age, enrolling with an online college is becoming more and more logical. With the responsibilities of everyday life taking precedence, being able to work in your own time from the comfort of your own home is a great necessity.\n\nWe know we may seem a bit biased. But here are some reasons why we think enrolling with an online college will be one of the best choices you make in 2018:\n<h3><strong>Availability</strong></h3>\nCampus educational institutions are limited to the number of students that they can house. Online colleges, however, aren?t bound by this restriction. Here at Open Study College, we have over 60,000 students enrolled, and offer the same great service to them all.\n<h3><strong>Convenience</strong></h3>\nNot only are you able to work at your own pace, you can work from wherever you wish. Most online courses can be downloaded or accessed on all computer devices; this could be your laptop in the comfort of your own home, or a portable tablet on your commute to work.\n<h3><strong>Variety</strong></h3>\nOnline colleges offer a wider range of subjects than campus institutes, as well as the option of studying as many different courses as you wish. Our choice of 450 courses vary from Accounting and Bookkeeping to Dog Grooming and Childcare to accommodate for all our students.\n<h3><strong>Cost</strong></h3>\nIt\'s a lot cheaper to study with an online college. As you don\'t need to pay added fees for other costs, your money goes solely towards the course materials and your personal tutor. With Open Study College, you can even set up a payment plan tospread the cost across an agreed time span.\n<h3><strong>Personal Growth</strong></h3>\nOnline learning is not for everyone; this type of learning does not suit some people. However, those who are find that their personal skills vastly improve. Skills such as:\n<ul>\n 	<li><strong>Timekeeping</strong> to keep on top of all your studying and deadlines</li>\n 	<li><strong>Organisation</strong> in order to manage your daily life as well as your studying</li>\n 	<li><strong>Self-motivation</strong> as you are in charge of your learning so you will need to push yourself to keep going</li>\n</ul>\nIf this sounds like something for you, then don?t hesitate to enrol with us.\n\nContact our Student Adviser team on <strong>03300 563100</strong>,to find the best course to suit your career needs. Alternatively, head over to our <strong><a href=\"https://www.openstudycollege.com/pages/how-it-works.html\">website</a> </strong>to browse and enrol today.',NULL,NULL,9,'2018-01-05 10:05:04','2018-01-05 10:05:04',2,'https://blog.openstudycollege.com/?p=7929',1,1,1,0,0,NULL,NULL),
