	(1487,'How to Bag a New Career','new-career',NULL,NULL,'<em>?Dear diary, </em>\n\n<em>I?ve only been back at work for a week and I am already in a bit of a slump. I no longer like my job. </em>\n\n<em>It?s time for a change; it?s time to focus on what makes me happy and work towards a career that I actually want to be in. </em>\n\n<em>We?re in 2018 now, so this is the perfect opportunity for me to make a change!</em>\n\n<em>But how??? </em>\n\n<strong>Confession Time:</strong> Does this sound like you?\n\nNo need to be embarrassed, we?ve all been there. But how many of us actually put these plans into action?\n\nIt may seem like a daunting task, but we\'ve got the best tips on how to bag yourself a new career:\n<ul>\n 	<li>\n<h3>Figure out <em>why</em> you want a new career</h3>\n</li>\n</ul>\nThis time of year is hard for everyone: the post-Christmas slump. So you need to decipher whether that?s the cause, or whether you have genuinely had enough. If it\'s the latter, then figure out what is about your job that you don?t like so you won?t fall into the same mistakes.\n<ul>\n 	<li>\n<h3>Put yourself out there</h3>\n</li>\n</ul>\nBe open to new opportunities. Through elimination you will be able to know what you <em>don?t</em> want and narrow the search. Also,services such as career guidance and recruitment agencieswill be able to help match you to the type of career youare suited for.\n<ul>\n 	<li>\n<h3>Do some research</h3>\n</li>\n</ul>\nOnce you have decided which career you are interested in, do some research on the best routes and opportunities that are available. This way you can find out which route works best for you, and get there much quicker!\n<ul>\n 	<li>\n<h3>Enrol on a course with Open Study College</h3>\n</li>\n</ul>\nWith over 450 different courses, we have somethingsuitable for everyone. Varying from Dog Grooming or Accounting and Bookkeeping, to Personal Training and Cake Making, our accredited qualifications and knowledge-based courses could be the first step towards your new, dream career.\n\n&nbsp;\n\nJoin over 60,00 students who have changed their lives with Open Study College. Take a look on our website, or give our Student Adviser team a call on <strong>03300 563100</strong> to enrol today!\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<a class=\"blog-cta\" href=\"https://www.openstudycollege.com/pages/how-it-works.html\">Enrol Now!</a>',NULL,NULL,9,'2018-01-08 11:00:59','2018-01-08 11:00:59',2,'https://blog.openstudycollege.com/?p=7940',1,1,1,0,0,NULL,NULL),
