	(1515,'What are ABE qualifications? Everything you need to know about ABE courses','7043-autosave-v1',NULL,NULL,'Having been around for over 40 years, ABE qualifications enablepeople from all over the world to gain the most up to date and dynamic skills on the market. Here?s everything you need to know about ABE qualifications and courses:\n<h2>What are ABE qualifications?</h2>\nEstablished in 1973, ABE provide high quality qualificationsworld wide in areas such as entrepreneurship, business start-up, business management, marketing, human resources, travel, tourism and hospitality management.\n\n<iframe class=\"youtube-video\" src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/216148349\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe>\n\nThese Ofqual regulated qualifications offer first-class, innovative education and work towards inspiring and empowering learners. Over 1.5 million people have improved their skills with an ABE qualification, and many have gone on to own a successful business. ABE qualifications are recognised by colleges, universities, employers and governments all around the world.\n<h2>How are ABE qualifications developed?</h2>\n<iframe class=\"youtube-video\" src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/216154106\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe>\n<h2>Who can study an ABE qualification?</h2>\nWith the help of distance learning, these qualifications are accessible in over 100 countries and this number is continually growing. Studying at home allows students to easily access ABE courses digitally via their devices from anywhere, at any time.\n<h2>Can I use these for entry into university?</h2>\nYes! ABE qualifications are accepted by over 80 different universities. Justwhat you need to fast-track onto a degree course.\n<h2>Why study an ABE course?</h2>\nAn ABE qualification is great for gaining a Ofqual recognised qualification in the business or travel and tourism industry.With aqualification from ABE on your CVyou will boost your chances of achieving your desired career. These qualifications will enable you to gain the most up to date and dynamic skills on the market.\n\n<iframe class=\"youtube-video\" src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/216159242\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe>\n<h2>Introducing our ABE Business Startup Course</h2>\n<iframe class=\"youtube-video\" src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/216166219\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe>\n\n<a class=\"blog-cta\" href=\"https://www.openstudycollege.com/qualifications/abe\">Take a look at our ABEqualifications and courses</a>',NULL,NULL,9,'2018-01-16 14:58:21','2018-01-16 14:58:21',1,'https://blog.openstudycollege.com/7043-autosave-v1/',1,1,1,0,0,NULL,NULL),
