you course.\n<ol start=\"5\">\n 	<li>\n<h2><strong>Study your way</strong></h2>\n</li>\n</ol>\nOur Addiction Counselling course is studied through distance learning, meaning you are able to study at your own pace and in your own time. There are no strict deadlines to adhere to, so you can make it work around you. You could even work simultaneously, meaning you can gain knowledge and experience at the same time.\n\nTake a look at our website or call our Student Adviser team on<strong> 03300 563100</strong>, and they will be able to help you enrol on our <a href=\"https://www.openstudycollege.com/courses/addiction-counselling.html\">Addiction Counselling course</a> today!',NULL,NULL,9,'2018-01-16 15:30:30','2018-01-16 15:30:30',1,'https://blog.openstudycollege.com/8006-revision-v1/',1,1,1,0,0,NULL,NULL),
