	(1638,'What Makes Distance Learning So Effective?','makes-distance-learning-effective',NULL,NULL,'Distance learning is becoming more and more popular in recent times.\n\nOver 207,000 students chose to study via distance learning last year, and over 60,000 students have previously enrolled with us at Open Study College.\n\n60,000 people surely can?t be wrong?\n\nSo what makes distance learning - particularly with Open Study College - so effective?\n<h2><strong>Is it the flexible schedule?</strong></h2>\nYou are in control of your own learning. Distance learning allows you to study at your own pace and in your own time, and to a schedule that works around you.\n\nIf you are a parent or working, you will be able to fit your learning in when you wish without disrupting your usual routine.\n<h2><strong>Is it the award-winning tutor support?</strong></h2>\nThroughout the duration of your course, you will be provided with a qualified and professional tutor for support. They are there to advise you and provide feedback, so you can achieve the best possible outcome in your studies.\n\nHere at Open Study College, we have <a href=\"https://www.openstudycollege.com/pages/tutors.html\">award winning tutors</a> that have received amazing feedback from our previous students; they are there to ensure you make the most of your courses.\n<h2><strong>Is it the great value for money?</strong></h2>\nAt Open Study College, our courses are offered at very affordable prices. Not only do we often have amazing discounts on some of our courses (like right now?), but we also offer affordable payment plans to help you spread the cost of your learning, making it more affordable.\n<h2><strong>Is it the wide range of courses and qualifications?</strong></h2>\nDistance learning allows you to choose from a varied selection of courses that can improve your career prospects. Studying from home offers you a wider selection of courses than if you were to study in an educational institution.\n\nIn addition, it is possible to study the same accredited qualifications that you would achieve in school or college right from the comfort of your own home.\n<h2><strong>Or could it be something else?</strong></h2>\nYou\'ll have to figure that out...\n\nIf you want to see why 60,000 students chose us and what makes distance learning so effective, give our Student Adviser team a call on<strong>03300 563100</strong>.\n\nAlternatively, check out our list of courses to see which distance learning course is perfect for you.\n\n<a class=\"blog-cta\" href=\"https://www.openstudycollege.com/pages/how-it-works.html\">Take a look at our courses</a>',NULL,NULL,9,'2018-03-05 11:07:56','2018-03-05 11:07:56',2,'https://blog.openstudycollege.com/?p=8241',1,1,1,0,0,NULL,NULL),
