	(1647,'Open study College are Shortlisted for Excellence in Customer Service','open-study-college-shortlisted-excellence-customer-service',NULL,NULL,'It looks like March is the month that just keeps on giving!\n\nPreviously, we mentioned that we had been nominated for two awards at the Business Master Awards 2018 West Midlands. But now, we have even more news?\n\nOpen Study College has been shortlisted for Excellence in Customer Service at the Greater Birmingham Chamber of Commerce Annual Awards!\n\nAs one of the most prestigious events in the area?s business calendar, the award?s dinner is due to attract more than 1,200 guests from the Greater Birmingham region for a night of dinner, drinks, awards and appreciation.\n<h2><strong>The Greater Birmingham Chamber of Commerce </strong></h2>\nThe Greater Birmingham Chamber of Commerce represents the voice of a wide group of businesses across Birmingham and its outer areas that aims to connect and support the growth of local businesses.\n\nWe at Open Study College are delighted at the news of another nomination, especially within the field of Customer Service. We take pride in ensuring that our students are provided with the best experience during their enrolments and studying with us; to know that our efforts have been recognised is an achievement in itself.\n\nThe event will be held at the International Convention Centre in Birmingham on Thursday 19<sup>th</sup> April 2018, and we are excited to dine amongst a vast collection of worthy nominees and fellow local businesses.',NULL,NULL,9,'2018-03-07 16:47:07','2018-03-07 16:47:07',2,'https://blog.openstudycollege.com/?p=8255',1,1,1,0,0,NULL,NULL),
