	(1705,'Have you heard about our new Online Business courses?','new-online-business-courses',NULL,NULL,'Have you heard about our new online Business courses?\n\nWe have been working on providing more qualifications in our most popular and requested areas; these courses have been part of the outcome.\n\nBut they aren?t as generic as they may sound?\n\nOnline Business courses may sound like the other distance learning courses we offer,but these are on a different level.\n<h2><strong>What makes these courses different?</strong></h2>\nThe new courses that we offer enable students to achieve much higher, accredited qualifications.\n\nAfter listening to feedback, we wanted to ensure that our range of courses catered to the needs of all our students, and that included offering courses on a higher level.\n\nThe different courses are equivalent to university level studying and can help you achieve part of your degree from the comfort of your own home!\n\nIn addition, the selection of courses varies throughout many aspects of business, so you can choose which area you wish to advance your career in.\n<h2><strong>Which online Business courses are available?</strong></h2>\nThere are a few categories in which these courses are available:\n\n<strong><u>Business Management University Foundation Programme Level 3 </u></strong>\n\n<strong><u>Business Management University 1st and 2nd Year Level 4 and 5</u></strong>\n\n<strong><u>IT and Computing University 1st and 2nd Year Level 4 and 5</u></strong>\n\n<strong><u>Sales and Marketing </u></strong><strong><u>University 1st and 2nd Year Level 4 and 5</u></strong>\n\n<strong><u>Leadership and Team Working </u></strong><strong><u>University 1st and 2nd Year Level 4 and 5</u></strong>\n\n<strong><u>Accounting and Finance </u></strong><strong><u>University 1st and 2nd Year Level 4 and 5</u></strong>\n\n<strong><u>Hotel and Hospitality </u></strong><strong><u>University 1st and 2nd Year Level 4 and 5</u></strong>\n\n<strong><u><a href=\"https://www.openstudycollege.com/courses/business-admin-management-6.html\">Business and Administrative Management Level 6 Postgraduate MBA Entry</a></u></strong>\n\n<strong><u>Business Strategic Management MBA Advanced Entry Level 7</u></strong>\n\n(The Level 4 and 5 courses are available as individual levels as well as a combined course.)\n\nEach course level is equivalent to a respective year at university and will provide you with the necessary credits to complete your degree. Upon completion of your course, you will be able to continue your studies at many UK universities to complete a Top-up course, allowing you to complete your degree.\n<h2><strong>How do I enrol? </strong></h2>\nEnrolment is just a click away!\n\nGive our Student Adviser team a call on <strong>03300 563100</strong> or check out the website to find out more about the courses.',NULL,NULL,9,'2018-04-05 10:02:08','2018-04-05 10:02:08',2,'https://blog.openstudycollege.com/?p=8359',1,1,1,0,0,NULL,NULL),
