	(1716,'Dreaming of becoming a Zookeeper? Study our Zoology course!','zookeeper-study-zoology-course',NULL,NULL,'Are you the type of person who wonders how a zebra got its stripes?\n\nOr what about how animals control their internal environment?\n\nMaybe your burning question is which came first, the chicken or the egg?\n\n?okay so maybe it can?t tell you everything, but our <a href=\"https://www.openstudycollege.com/courses/zoology-level-3.html\">Zoology course</a> is a great place to start.\n<h2><strong>What is Zoology? </strong></h2>\nZoology incorporates all aspects of animal biology and historical origins, including:\n<ul>\n 	<li>Organisms</li>\n 	<li>Evolution</li>\n 	<li>Vertebrates</li>\n 	<li>Invertebrates</li>\n 	<li>Taxonomy</li>\n 	<li>Species</li>\n 	<li>Reproduction</li>\n 	<li>The Animal Kingdom</li>\n</ul>\n?the list goes on.\n\nIf you are looking for a career working with animals, then this is the perfect course for you.\n\nThis Level 3 Zoology course uncovers animal behaviours and habitats and expands your theory knowledge of the subject.\n\nThis course will provide you with the knowledge and skills to flourish in this sector, whether to go onto further learning or gain experience in an animal environment.\n<h2><strong>Career Prospects</strong></h2>\nOnce you have completed this course, you will be awarded with a Certificate of Achievement from ABC Awards. ABC Awards are a nationally-recognised awarding organisation with a range of Ofqual-regulated qualifications and years of experience.\n\nUpon receiving this certificate, you will be able to further your experience and knowledge and go on to a range of different careers.\n\nMany people who choose to study this course have go on to thrive in many different careers. Some include working in animal shelters, veterinary practices or rescue centres.\n\nThe starting salary for these careers can range from 25-30,000 and rise to anything over 60,000!\n<h2><strong>Why study with Open Study College?</strong></h2>\n<ul>\n 	<li>Bench-marked against Ofqual Level 3 standards</li>\n 	<li><a href=\"https://www.openstudycollege.com/pages/tutors.html\">Award-winning tutor support</a></li>\n 	<li>Free added perks like an NUS Extra card and cool stationary</li>\n 	<li>Study at your own pace in your own time</li>\n 	<li><a href=\"https://blog.openstudycollege.com/tag/awards/\">Award-winning college</a></li>\n</ul>\nSounds like a pretty good deal right?\n\nTo start your new career today, give our Student Adviser team a call on <strong>03300 563100</strong>. Or enrol on our <a href=\"https://www.openstudycollege.com/pages/how-it-works.html\">website</a> at just the click of a button.',NULL,NULL,9,'2018-04-09 10:14:35','2018-04-09 10:16:30',2,'https://blog.openstudycollege.com/?p=8373',1,1,1,0,0,NULL,NULL),
