	(1747,'Dreaming of setting up your own business?','setting-up-business',NULL,NULL,'<h2>Picture this?</h2>\nIt?s 6.30am.\n\nYou get out of bed after hitting snooze for the 6<sup>th</sup> and final time.\n\nOnce you head downstairs, you brush your teeth, put your lunch into your bag and make yourself a coffee to go.\n\nYou pick up your gym bag and head to the car.\n\nOn your way there you get caught in 20-minute congestion because every other single person just like you decided to leave the house at the same time so now you?re all stuck on the same road at the same time, probably trying to get to the same place.\n\nYou get to work with barely any time to spare but make it to your desk with 3 minutes to go so your boss can?t complain.\n\nThe day passes by. Meetings and coffees, coffees and reports, reports and emails. All the while you dream of setting up your own businesswhich seems to get further and further away each day.\n\nYou make it to 5pm and head to your car to sit in another stint of follow-the-leader traffic.\n\nYou make it to the gym. It?s pretty busy. You stick to one cardio machine while catching up on an episode of Eastenders.\n\nOnce you?re done you head home and have dinner. Maybe a freshly cooked meal?most likely a takeaway (you did just go to the gym so you deserve it, right...?)\n\nAfter hours of soulless television, it hits 11pm and its time to go to bed.\n\nWake up. Repeat.\n\n&nbsp;\n\nNow, we don?t know about you? but this is not the life we would choose.\n\nLiving each day in a repetitive cycle of work, gym, eat, repeat.\n\nWouldn?t you want some more excitement in your life? A bit of variety, a change, to make your own schedule?\n\nThen it?s time to make that dream of setting up your own business into a reality.\n<h2>Setting Up Your Own Business</h2>\n<ul>\n 	<li>Make your own hours</li>\n 	<li>Work from home if you want to</li>\n 	<li>Do something you LOVE!</li>\n 	<li>BE HAPPY!</li>\n</ul>\nAt Open Study College, we want to help you get there.\n\nOur <span style=\"text-decoration: underline\"><a href=\"https://www.openstudycollege.com/courses/abe-business-startup-3.html\">ABE Level 3 Certificate in Business Start-Up</a></span> is the best choice to help you to get started.\n\nThis Level 3 course is certified by ABE (The Association of Business Executives) and reveals all the key elements of what it takes to begin setting up your own business.\n<ul>\n 	<li>Background knowledge and market potential</li>\n 	<li>Building and developing your ideas</li>\n 	<li>Marketing</li>\n 	<li>Planning</li>\n 	<li>Finance and budgeting</li>\n</ul>\n?and so much more.\n\nIt is all you need to get started. Turn your passion into your career.\n\nThink you could be your own boss?\n\nTake a look at our <span style=\"text-decoration: underline\"><a href=\"https://www.openstudycollege.com/pages/how-it-works.html\">website</a></span> to see the choice of courses, or call our Student Adviser team on <strong>033300 563 100</strong>.',NULL,NULL,9,'2018-04-24 10:00:37','2018-04-24 10:00:37',2,'https://blog.openstudycollege.com/?p=8422',1,1,1,0,0,NULL,NULL),
