	(1780,'Improve your knowledge of conflict management in the workplace','conflict-management-workplace',NULL,NULL,'As much as we would like, everyone doesn?t always get along.\n\nWhether it be difference of opinion, clashing personalities or a full-blown feud, there will always be people that don?t get along.\n\nNow imagine having to see these people day in and day out? not ideal really.\n\nWell that?s what it would be like to dislike someone in the workplace. You would be in their presence for most of each day, 5 days a week, year after year.\n\nBut that?s natural. It is bound to happen and there is not much that we can do to stop it.\n\nHowever, how we deal with this conflict in the workplace can make a big difference, which is why conflict management is so vital in every working environment.\n<h2><strong>What is conflict management?</strong></h2>\nConflict management is the system of controlling the amount of conflict within a workplace, and knowing how to deal with it correctly when it does occur.\n\nThis includes all stages of the process:\n<ul>\n 	<li>Identifying candidates who would work well in a team during the interview and recruitment process</li>\n 	<li>Know and understand the purpose of competence and competences within a workplace</li>\n 	<li>Actions to take to avoid conflict</li>\n 	<li>Actions to take once conflict has been recognised</li>\n 	<li>Understanding the role a manager plays in conflict management</li>\n 	<li>Legal obligations</li>\n</ul>\nThis is vital within a workplace and is usually the responsibility of the HR Personnel.\n<h2><strong>How can I learn more about conflict management?</strong></h2>\nAt Open Study College, we have a course that is perfect for you in regard to improving these skills.\n\nOur <a href=\"https://www.openstudycollege.com/courses/managing-conflict-in-the-workplace-3.html\"><strong><u>Managing Conflict in the Workplace Level 3</u></strong></a> covers all of these skills, in addition to providing you with a Certificate of Achievement to support your knowledge.\n\nThis is a great addition to have on your CV as many employers find it hard to find employees with these skills, so you will stand out within the crowd. This increases your employability and could even result in an increased salary!\n\nSound like something you could do?\n\nCheck out the course on our <a href=\"https://www.openstudycollege.com/\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline\"><strong>website</strong></span></a> or call our Student Adviser team on<strong>03300 563 100</strong> to enrol today!\n\n&nbsp;',NULL,NULL,9,'2018-05-08 17:08:29','2018-05-08 17:09:04',2,'https://blog.openstudycollege.com/?p=8475',1,1,1,0,0,NULL,NULL),
