	(1794,'Could a career in nursing be perfect for you?','career-in-nursing',NULL,NULL,'Rewarding?\n\nChallenging?\n\nInteresting?\n\nIs that what you think of when you think of your career?\n\nIf not, then perhaps it?s not the career for you.\n\nBut what if we could promise you that a <strong>career in nursing</strong> will offer you all of this and more??\n<h2><strong>Rewarding</strong></h2>\nNursing is one of the world?s most rewarding careers. Throughout your career, you will get to meet an indefinite number of people, help bring new life into the world, and go home knowing that you have helped thousands of people with their health.\n<h2><strong>Challenging</strong></h2>\nThe journey to becoming a nurse is not an easy one.\n\nEntry requirements can vary depending on the course you choose to take, but the typical requirements are often at least 2 (but preferably 3) A Levels or equivalent with supporting GCSEs; at least one of these must be in Biology or a similar science.\n<h2><strong>Interesting</strong></h2>\nIt may be challenging but it is all worth it.\n\nThe daily routine of a nurse never stays the same. One day you could be taking a blood sample in a GP surgery, and the next you could be visiting a nursing or residential home. Some even choose to become a nurse in the military!\n\nThe skillset and capabilities of a nurse allows you to vary your job role and perform to the highest standard in any environment necessary.\n\nCould you say this about your current job role?\n\nA career in nursing is a lot more than just a job; it?s a lifestyle.\n\nYou need to be dedicated and willing to put in the hours.\n\nYou need to love what you do.\n\nIf this sounds like you, then a career in nursing could be perfect.\n\nTake a look at the <a href=\"https://www.openstudycollege.com/qualifications/a-level\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline\"><strong>A Levels</strong></span></a> and <a href=\"https://www.openstudycollege.com/qualifications/igcse\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline\"><strong>GCSEs</strong></span></a> we offer to help kickstart your career in one of the best professions in the world.\n\nOr call our Student Adviser team on <strong>03300 563 100</strong> to discuss your options and enrol today!',NULL,NULL,9,'2018-05-11 10:10:55','2018-05-11 10:10:55',2,'https://blog.openstudycollege.com/?p=8493',1,1,1,0,0,NULL,NULL),
