	(1800,'Feeling creative? Find out how to make jewellery','creative-make-jewellery',NULL,NULL,'It?s getting to that time of year where the sun makes us all re-evaluate our lives.\n\nNo one wants to be stuck at a desk all day, staring blankly into a computer screen when we could be outside enjoying the sunshine.\n\nOr you may even just generally be bored.\n\nThe human race has a general attraction to the outdoors when it is sunny outside, and will find any excuse to bask in it.\n\nWhether it be a new job or a new hobby, it?s time to make a change.\n<h2><strong>Why not learn how to make jewellery? </strong></h2>\nJewellery making is a refined and creative skill. You need creativity and technique to understand what is required to make jewellery, as well as design your own.\n\nIt can also benefit you in more ways than one:\n<ul>\n 	<li>\n<h4><strong>It releases any unwelcomed energy </strong></h4>\n</li>\n</ul>\nIf you are stressed, angry or upset, having a creative outlet can often ease these emotions. Your energy will be focused on the hobby as opposed to what is causing your frustrations.\n<ul>\n 	<li>\n<h4><strong>It reveals any hidden talents</strong></h4>\n</li>\n</ul>\nFor all you know, you could be a Swarovski in the making; but you will never know until you try. Learning how to make jewellery may reveal a hidden passion or talent that you may never have known that you have.\n<ul>\n 	<li>\n<h4><strong>It cures boredom</strong></h4>\n</li>\n</ul>\nIf you?re ever bored or stuck for something to do, taking up a creative hobby will fill any spare time that you may have. You?ll never be bored again!\n<ul>\n 	<li>\n<h4><strong>You will never have to buy jewellery again</strong></h4>\n</li>\n</ul>\nHaving such a creative hobby can also save you a lot of money. You?ll be able to make your own jewellery as well as make it for others (saves you a lot of money on gifts!)\n\nOur <a href=\"https://www.openstudycollege.com/courses/jewellery-making.html\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline\"><strong>Jewellery Making course</strong></span></a> can help you.\n\nThis level 2 course covers everything from the origins of jewellery making, to equipment and techniques ? everything you need to get you started.\n\nCall our Student Adviser team to enrol today, or check out all of our Creative courses available on our website.',NULL,NULL,9,'2018-05-15 09:19:19','2018-05-15 09:19:19',2,'https://blog.openstudycollege.com/?p=8501',1,1,1,0,0,NULL,NULL),
