o practice and ensure that you understand everything that you have learned.\n<ul>\n 	<li>\n<h2><strong>Distance learning means you are in control </strong></h2>\n</li>\n</ul>\nYou are in control of your own learning.\n\nStudy anywhere and at any time at a pace that suits you. You will even receive tutor support to help you through your studies.\n\nSound interesting?\n\nThen take a look at the <a href=\"https://www.openstudycollege.com/courses/advanced-foot-health-practice.html\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>Diploma in Advanced Foot Health Practice</strong></span></a> course on our website. Or call our student adviser team on <strong>03300 563 100</strong>.',NULL,NULL,9,'2018-05-23 09:02:34','2018-11-05 12:07:29',1,'https://blog.openstudycollege.com/?p=8518',1,1,1,0,0,NULL,NULL),
