	(1825,'5 Reasons to Study Business Management','5-reasons-study-business-management-2',NULL,NULL,'<blockquote><strong><em>Business Management </em></strong><em>? The activities associated with running a company.</em></blockquote>\nQuite generic if you ask us.\n\nThere is no specified occupation? no profession title? no detailed trade?\n\nIf you think about it, business management is applicable to us all, regardless of our career choice.\n\nIt?s an ideal choice for those who want to progress in their career or develop their current understanding. When you study business management, you learn all aspects of a business from marketing to finance, customer service and administration, making it easier to know what is needed for a thriving business.\n\nInterested? Then here?s 5 reasons why you should study business management.\n<ul>\n 	<li>\n<h2><strong>Experience alone is not enough</strong></h2>\n</li>\n</ul>\nAlthough you often hear the contrary of education not being enough, it works for experience too. Experience can only get you so far. Once you progress within your career, there will be aspects that you will be expected to know or contribute that experience won?t be able to give you. Things like development strategies, influential ideas and foresight ? all of which cannot be developed through experience alone.\n<ul>\n 	<li>\n<h2><strong>Your ability is hindered by your current role</strong></h2>\n</li>\n</ul>\nIn most cases, your current role will be perfect for you - this is why you got the job! But to be able to progress within a business, you need to know more than just your own sector of the company. If you plan to ever become self-employed or a working your way up the corporate ladder, knowing all areas of the company are vital.\n<ul>\n 	<li>\n<h2><strong>It is flexible to all career choices</strong></h2>\n</li>\n</ul>\nWhen you study business management, you are studying the general working activity of how a business operates. This could mean any business. The main components of all careers will be built on the same business foundation.\n<ul>\n 	<li>\n<h2><strong>Indefinite salary expectations </strong></h2>\n</li>\n</ul>\nIt?s hard to give a definite figure of salary expectations of those who study business management. But if you think about it, it is limitless. Business management will allow you to climb the career ladder and progress, which will result in a continuously growing salary.\n<ul>\n 	<li>\n<h2><strong>Learn at your own pace</strong></h2>\n</li>\n</ul>\nThanks to distance learning, you can now study business management from the comfort of your own home and at your own pace. This allows you to work while you learn, giving you the opportunity to gain experience and knowledge at the same time.\n\nThink business management could be for you? Head over to our <a href=\"https://www.openstudycollege.com/business_courses.html\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline\"><strong>website</strong></span></a> to check out all the available courses we have to offer.\n\nOr call our student adviser team on <strong>03300 563 100</strong> to discuss your options and enrol today!',NULL,NULL,9,'2018-05-30 15:48:13','2018-05-30 15:48:13',2,'https://blog.openstudycollege.com/?p=8538',1,1,1,0,0,NULL,NULL),
