	(1829,'Develop your leadership skills with us!','develop-leadership-skills',NULL,NULL,'Leadership skills are not something that everyone naturally possesses, but they are something that everyone must take on at some point in their career.\n\nIf you want to progress within a career, there will always come a time when you will need to put your leadership qualities into action.\n\nIt takes experience, knowledge and understanding to develop leadership skills.\n\nThanks to Open Study College with the help of our distance learning courses, you can do just this.\n<h2><strong>Which courses are available?</strong></h2>\nThe qualifications range in level to accommodate for your education and career needs. At Open Study College, we offer the following courses:\n\n<a href=\"https://www.openstudycollege.com/courses/ilm-award-in-leadership-and-management.html\"><strong><u>ILM Level 3 Award in Leadership and Management</u></strong></a>\n\nThis Award is suitable for those who want to learn the basics of what it takes to be a good leader.\n\n<a href=\"https://www.openstudycollege.com/courses/ilm-cert-leadership-and-management.html\"><strong><u>ILM Level 3 Certificate in Leadership and Management</u></strong></a>\n\nSimilar to the Award, this Certificate enhances knowledge and is perfect for those in a managerial position who want to progress their career.\n\nILM (The Institute of Leadership and Management) is the UK?s leading provider of leadership, management and coaching qualifications, with over 50 years ofexperience in learning and development.\n\nTheyspecialise in developing flexible learning programmes that deliver essential leadership and management skills into the heart of organisations.\n\nOr if you want to continue your education further, we also offer courses that provide you with the equivalent of the first two years of university:\n\n<span style=\"text-decoration: underline\"><strong><a href=\"https://www.openstudycollege.com/courses/leadership-team-working.html\">Leadership and Team Working University 1st and 2nd Year Level 4 and 5</a></strong></span>\n\nMaybeyou just want to touch up your skills, then our<span style=\"text-decoration: underline\"><strong><a href=\"https://www.openstudycollege.com/courses/developing-leadership-skills-3.html\">Developing Leadership Skills Level 3</a></strong></span> courseis for you.\n\nAllcourses touch on the vital qualities and responsibilities of being a manager, such as:\n<ul>\n 	<li>Communication</li>\n 	<li>Motivation</li>\n 	<li>Resolving conflict</li>\n 	<li>Making decisions</li>\n</ul>\nNo matter which industry you work in, you can always benefit from improving your knowledge and leadership skills.\n\nTake the next step on your personal career ladder and enrol on our website.\n\nOr call our student adviser team on <strong>03300 563100</strong> to start your career progression today.',NULL,NULL,9,'2018-05-31 10:03:48','2018-05-31 13:00:01',2,'https://blog.openstudycollege.com/?p=8543',1,1,1,0,0,NULL,NULL),
