mple, in a school or nursery or, of course, a child psychologist.\n<ul>\n 	<li>\n<h2>A financial investment</h2>\n</li>\n</ul>\nDid you know that working as a psychologist can have very rewarding salary benefits? Once you have officially qualified as a child psychologist, you can earn anything up from a starting salary of 27,000!\n\nIn addition,if you decide to specialise, you can earn study grants and bonuses to aid your continued learning.\n\nSounds like a great choice to us!\n\nWe offer a range of courses including<span style=\"text-decoration: underline\"><strong><a href=\"https://www.openstudycollege.com/courses/ocn-child-psychology-course.html\">Child Psychology Level 3</a></strong></span>,<span style=\"text-decoration: underline\"><strong><a href=\"https://www.openstudycollege.com/courses/early-years-and-child-psychology-3.html\">Early Years and Child Psychology Level 3</a></strong></span><span style=\"text-decoration: underline\"><strong>,</strong></span><span style=\"text-decoration: underline\"><strong><a href=\"https://www.openstudycollege.com/courses/child-care-child-psychology.html\">Child Care and Child Psychology Level 3</a></strong></span>that can help you work towards the career of your dreams.\n\nIf this sounds like something you would be interested in, call our student adviser team on <strong>03300 563100</strong> to get more information.\n\nOr take a look at our website to see what ourChild Psychology course has to offer.\n\n&nbsp;',NULL,NULL,9,'2018-05-31 12:34:15','2018-05-31 12:34:15',1,'https://blog.openstudycollege.com/8547-revision-v1/',1,1,1,0,0,NULL,NULL),
	(1835,'Develop your leadership skills with us!','8543-autosave-v1',NULL,NULL,'Leadership skills are not something that everyone naturally possesses, but they are something that everyone must take on at some point in their career.\n\nIf you want to progress within a career, there will always come a time when you will need to put your leadership qualities into action.\n\nIt takes experience, knowledge and understanding to develop leadership skills.\n\nThanks to Open Study College with the help of our distance learning courses, you can do just this.\n<h2><strong>Which courses are available?</strong></h2>\n&nbsp;\n\nThe qualifications range in level to accommodate for your education and career needs. At Open Study College, we offer the following courses:\n\n<a href=\"https://www.openstudycollege.com/courses/ilm-award-in-leadership-and-management.html\"><strong><u>ILM Level 3 Award in Leadership and Management</u></strong></a>\n\nThis Award is suitable for those who want to learn the basics of what it takes to be a good leader.\n\n<a href=\"https://www.openstudycollege.com/courses/ilm-cert-leadership-and-management.html\"><strong><u>ILM Level 3 Certificate in Leadership and Management</u></strong></a>\n\nSimilar to the Award, this Certificate enhances knowledge and is perfect for those in a managerial position who want to progress their career.\n\nILM (The Institute of Leadership and Management) is the UK?s leading provider of leadership, management and coaching qualifications, with over 50 years ofexperience in learning and development.\n\nTheyspecialise in developing flexible learning programmes that deliver essential leadership and management skills into the heart of organisations.\n\nOr if you want to continue your education further, we also offer courses that provide you with the equivalent of the first two years of university:\n\n<span style=\"text-decoration: underline\"><strong><a href=\"https://www.openstudycollege.com/courses/leadership-team-working.html\">Lea