	(1849,'Why You Should Study Animal Welfare','study-animal-welfare',NULL,NULL,'In this current generation, animals have almost the same rights as humans.\n\nWith a world full of vegetarians, vegans and animal rights? protestors, the politics behind animal farming and care has brought about much conversation.\n\nBut not just that, for the other portion of society, it?s nice to know how animals are being cared for and what we can do to preserve their lives.\n\nAre you involved in the conversation?\n\nYou should be. And you could be when you study animal welfare:\n<ul>\n 	<li>\n<h2><strong>Learn more about animals</strong></h2>\n</li>\n</ul>\nIf you?re like us (and probably most of the human race), you love animals. Well this course allows you to dive deeper into the care and ethics of animals ? and to do that you will need to learn a bit more about them.\n<ul>\n 	<li>\n<h2><strong>Learn more about politics</strong></h2>\n</li>\n</ul>\nNot only will you get the chance to learn more about animals, this animal welfare course will allow you to brush up on your political skills. Discuss legal, ethical and commercial politics that surround animal welfare and what we can do to help.\n<ul>\n 	<li>\n<h2><strong>Career prospects</strong></h2>\n</li>\n</ul>\nOur animal welfare course provides a strong foundation to build your career upon. Many who choose to study this course have gone on to become veterinarians, zoologists and even lawyers.\n<ul>\n 	<li>\n<h2><strong>Study at your own pace in your own time</strong></h2>\n</li>\n</ul>\nThrough distance learning you will be able to study when and how you choose. Whether you want to study in your bedroom, your garden or even on the beach, you are in control of your own learning.\n<ul>\n 	<li>\n<h2><strong>Dedicated tutor support</strong></h2>\n</li>\n</ul>\nOur team of tutors, including award-winning tutor, Caroline Wren, are there to help you every step of the way. This way you can achieve the best possible grade to further your career.\n\nSo if you want to be a part of the conversation, check out our <a href=\"https://www.openstudycollege.com/courses/animal-welfare-4.html\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline\"><strong>Animal Welfare Level 4</strong></span></a> course online. Or call our student adviser team on <strong>03300 563 100</strong> to enrol today!\n\n&nbsp;',NULL,NULL,9,'2018-06-13 09:17:51','2018-06-13 09:17:51',2,'https://blog.openstudycollege.com/?p=8575',1,1,1,0,0,NULL,NULL),
