	(1862,'5 Key Benefits of Lifelong Learning','lifelong-learning-benefits',NULL,NULL,'Lifelong learning should be a key staple in your career and development plan.\n\nGrowing old is mandatory. But how you do so is optional.\n\nThere isn?t a set of rules that we must all abide by as we grow older.\n\nWho says we must stop going out and having fun?\n\nWho says we need to start resting more and going to bed earlier?\n\nAnd who says that we can?t continue learning and wanting to do better?\n\nIf anything, the latter is made for us ? they do say wisdom comes with age, so learning is not restricted by age.\n\nThis is the motto we like to live by here at Open Study College, because you?re never too old to study. This is why lifelong learning is so important.\n<h2><strong>Benefits of lifelong learning</strong></h2>\n<ul>\n 	<li>At an older age you are more focused and know what you want to do; choosing a course will be easy and you can commit to your learning.</li>\n 	<li>You are older so have more logic and common sense which helps in a lot of subjects.</li>\n 	<li>Employers will appreciate your studying more as it shows commitment to learning and increases your chances of being hired.</li>\n 	<li>Your conversation and communication will thrive.</li>\n 	<li>You will benefit both spiritually and mentally.</li>\n</ul>\nSo, don?t let a number hold you back from furthering your education or achieving a dream.\n\nLet a distance learning course from Open Study College help you push through that age barrier and continue your learning into the later stages of your life.\n\nIt?s up to you what you study. Our range of distance learning courses can help you develop your knowledge and improve your career at any age.\n\nWhether you are interested in <span style=\"text-decoration: underline\"><a href=\"https://www.openstudycollege.com/counselling_courses.html\"><strong>Counselling</strong></a></span> or <span style=\"text-decoration: underline\"><a href=\"https://www.openstudycollege.com/beauty-therapy_courses.html\"><strong>Beauty Therapy</strong></a></span>, <span style=\"text-decoration: underline\"><a href=\"https://www.openstudycollege.com/courses/floristry-practical-training.html\"><strong>Floristry</strong></a></span> or <span style=\"text-decoration: underline\"><a href=\"https://www.openstudycollege.com/fitness_courses.html\"><strong>Personal Training</strong></a></span>, we have a course that can assist your lifelong learning.\n\nVisit our website to download your copy of our prospectus, or call our student adviser team on <strong>03300 563 100</strong> to discuss your options and enrol today!\n\n&nbsp;',NULL,NULL,9,'2018-06-20 09:35:56','2018-06-20 09:35:56',2,'https://blog.openstudycollege.com/?p=8592',1,1,1,0,0,NULL,NULL),
