	(1865,'5 Reasons to Boost Your Accounting and Bookkeeping Knowledge','accounting-and-bookkeeping-knowledge',NULL,NULL,'It?s all well and good telling you that studying a distance learning course in Accounting and Bookkeeping will benefit you?\n\n?but unless you know why, are you actually going to click enrol without hesitation?\n\nWe doubt it. And we don?t blame you.\n\nYou wouldn?t buy a new TV without hearing all of the HD features or screen size. So why would you enrol onto a course without knowing what you get out of it first?\n\nExactly? you wouldn?t.\n\nSo we?re telling you the reasons you should boost your Accounting and Bookkeeping knowledge with our distance learning courses, so you don?t have to worry:\n<ul>\n 	<li>\n<h3><strong>Boost your CV</strong></h3>\n</li>\n</ul>\nHaving additional qualifications on your CV allows you to stand out within the crowd against those that just show standard or compulsory qualifications. It shows future employers that you are dedicated to your career as you have taken the initiative to study in your own time.\n<ul>\n 	<li>\n<h3><strong>More ability and enjoyment </strong></h3>\n</li>\n</ul>\nHaving more knowledge of accounting and bookkeeping will enable you to perform your role at a better standard. If you find you job less challenging, this may increase the amount of enjoyment you take from it, too.\n<ul>\n 	<li>\n<h3><strong>Do it in your spare time </strong></h3>\n</li>\n</ul>\nDistance learning courses mean that you can study when and where you choose. You won?t miss out on your daily responsibilities and social life as you can fit your studies in when suits you best.\n<ul>\n 	<li>\n<h3><strong>Improve your employability </strong></h3>\n</li>\n</ul>\nBy improving your accounting and bookkeeping knowledge, you will be capable of more and therefore more deserving of higher roles or new opportunities.\n<ul>\n 	<li>\n<h3><strong>Wide range of courses </strong></h3>\n</li>\n</ul>\nWith several accredited awarding bodies a