	(1901,'Choosing Distance Learning over Traditional Colleges','choosing-distance-learning',NULL,NULL,'More and more people are choosing distance learning over traditional colleges in the modern day education world.\n\nOver 63,000 students have chosen to study with us at Open Study College, with over 10,000 of them enrolling in the last year alone.\n\nMany people are quite sceptical of distance learning, as colleges have been the norm for many years. But that doesn?t mean that it is the best option for you.\n\nDo you know all the benefits of distance learning over traditional college??\n<h2>Traditional Colleges vs. Distance Learning</h2>\n<a href=\"/storage/images/media_items/old_images/2018/07/Choosing-Distance-Learning-Graph-19.07-2.png\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-8676\" src=\"/storage/images/media_items/old_images/2018/07/Choosing-Distance-Learning-Graph-19.07-2.png\" alt=\"Choosing Distance Learning over Traditional Colleges\" width=\"818\" height=\"722\" /></a>\n\nDon?t believe us? Check out our <a href=\"https://www.openstudycollege.com/pages/how-it-works.html\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline\">website</span></a> to see all our courses and see why choosing distance learning is the best option for your education and career.\n\nWe have great discounts on a wide range of our courses, so now really is the best time to enrol.\n\nWe know what we would do?\n\nAlternatively, call our Student Adviser team on <strong>03300 563100</strong> to enrol on your dream course today!',NULL,NULL,9,'2018-07-23 16:18:27','2018-07-23 16:26:31',2,'https://blog.openstudycollege.com/?p=8669',1,1,1,0,0,NULL,NULL),
