ining</strong> and designing <strong>exercise programmes</strong>.\n<h2><strong>Why Choose Open Study College? </strong></h2>\nOpen Study College is one of the UK?s leading distance learning providers with over 11 years? worth of experience in the industry. During this time, more 73,000 students have furthered their education and developed their career prospects by studying a course or qualification with us.\n\nWith a varied range of qualifications, such as A Levels, GCSEs, CACHE and ICB qualifications, this way of studying offers endless opportunities to all students.\n<ul>\n 	<li><strong>Flexible &amp; Convenient</strong></li>\n 	<li><strong>Affordable Study</strong></li>\n 	<li><strong>Unlimited Tutor Support</strong></li>\n 	<li><strong>Student Perks</strong></li>\n</ul>\nDon?t think you have to follow the same path that has been paved for you; you are more than capable of paving your own.\n\nIf you need any more information or help with choosing your options, call our student adviser team on <strong>03300 563 100</strong> who will be more than happy to help. Or head over to our website to see all the qualifications and courses that can help your career.\n\n<strong><a class=\"blog-cta\" href=\"https://www.openstudycollege.com/pages/how-it-works.html\">Take a look at our courses</a>  </strong>',NULL,NULL,9,'2018-08-17 09:23:48','2018-08-17 09:23:48',1,'https://blog.openstudycollege.com/8764-revision-v1/',1,1,1,0,0,NULL,NULL),
