	(1983,'10 Reasons to Study With Open Study College This Winter','7854-autosave-v1',NULL,NULL,'&nbsp;\n\nBut how many of us have kept up the resolutions that were set this at the start of this year??\n\nAccording to stats, starting the gym is the most popular New Year\'s resolution in the UK. But<strong>4%</strong> of New Year gym-goers do not make it to the end of January, and <strong>14%</strong> of the rest drop out before the end of February.\n\n<strong>?<em>It?s too cold? I woke up late? I?ll have a salad for lunch, then it will make up for not going?</em>?</strong>\n\nSound familiar?\n\nWe?ve all made at least one of these excuses while trying to avoid the gym.\n\nSo why not set a resolution that you can stick to, and study with Open Study College this winter. With so many great reasons to do it, any excuses are null and void.\n<ul>\n 	<li>\n<h3>Over 50<strong>0 varied courses</strong> to choose from</h3>\n</li>\n</ul>\nWhether you want to study a Childcare, Accounting &amp; Bookkeeping or Dog Grooming course, there are multiple options that will suit you and your career needs.\n<ul>\n 	<li>\n<h3><strong>Study at your own pace</strong> without following strict deadlines</h3>\n</li>\n</ul>\nDistance learning is scheduled around you. Work around your work and home life in your own time.\n<ul>\n 	<li>\n<h3><strong>Affordable prices</strong> with a pay monthly plan option</h3>\n</li>\n</ul>\nOur low prices are affordable, and can be paid through a low-cost monthly finance plan to pay as you study.\n<ul>\n 	<li>\n<h3>Award-winning <strong>tutor support</strong> throughout your course</h3>\n</li>\n</ul>\nYou will be assigned to a personal tutor who will assess and guide you through your course, and help you with any problems that arise.\n<ul>\n 	<li>\n<h3>Online and study pack format available</h3>\n</li>\n</ul>\nStudy in the best way for you ? either online or with a study pack sent to your home with added extras to help you along the way.\n<ul>\n 	<li>\n<h3><strong>FREE</strong> NUS Extra card for special student discounts</h3>\n</li>\n</ul>\nBenefit just like other students with a free NUS Extra card that gives you access to discounts and more\n<ul>\n 	<li>\n<h3>Accredited courses such as <strong>CACHE, AAT and Active IQ</strong></h3>\n</li>\n</ul>\nBoost your CV and career prospects with accredited qualifications from internationally recognised organisations\n<ul>\n 	<li>\n<h3><strong>Study anywhere</strong>, even from the comfort of your own home</h3>\n</li>\n</ul>\nTake your laptop, tablet or course study pack with you anywhere. Or stay right at home and feel comfortable while you learn.\n<ul>\n 	<li>\n<h3><strong>Academic support</strong> for any queries you may have</h3>\n</li>\n</ul>\nOur Student Adviser team can help you with choosing a course and enrolment, and our Student Services team will be there to help you with any queries you may have once you have started the course\n<ul>\n 	<li>\n<h3><strong>FREE</strong> CV Writing Service</h3>\n</li>\n</ul>\nAllow us to transform your CV with our professional writing service to give you the best career prospects possible.\n\nDon?t put off starting your dream career. Call our qualified Student Adviser team on <strong>03300 563100</strong>, or visit our <a href=\"https://www.openstudycollege.com/\"><strong><u>website</u></strong></a> to study with Open Study College this winter.\n\n<a class=\"blog-cta\" href=\"https://www.openstudycollege.com/pages/how-it-works.html\">Enrol Now &gt;&gt;</a>',NULL,NULL,9,'2018-10-30 10:53:28','2018-10-30 10:53:28',1,'https://blog.openstudycollege.com/7854-autosave-v1/',1,1,1,0,0,NULL,NULL),
	(1984,'Course of the Month: Introduction to Web Design Level 3','course-month-web-design',NULL,NULL,'How many times a day do you access a website?\n\nIt could be a retail website to do your online shopping, a newspaper website to keep up with daily stories, or even your favourite distance learning college website to read a blog article.\n\nWe do it without even realising, which is why it plays such a large and vital role.\n\nMore and more websites are being created and therefore more and more web designers are needed to create them.\n\nAt Open Study College, we aim to continually update our courses to cater to the needs of our students. Therefore, we would like to introduce one of our newest courses, and November?s Course of the Month?\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.openstudycollege.com/courses/intro-web-design\"><strong>Introduction to Web Design Level 3</strong></a></h2>\nThis beginner?s level course is the perfect introduction to the fundamentals of web design.\n<ul>\n 	<li>Explore the basics of web design</li>\n 	<li>Learn the role of a web designer in creating a successful business</li>\n 	<li>Develop a basic knowledge of HTML and CSS</li>\n</ul>\nBy studying this course, you will gain the essential skills to design, produce and deliver a basic website. And we can think of a few reasons why you need these skills:\n<h3><strong>Self-employment</strong></h3>\nEver thought about being your own boss?\n\nTo successfully start your own business, you will need to know all aspects; this includes web design. You will have complete agency over the design and capabilities of the website because it will be you who will be able to build it.\n\nOr maybe your new business <em>is</em> web design. A web designer will need to have the best website to showcase their talents to potential new clients.\n<h3><strong>Showcase your brand</strong></h3>\nAs a company, your website is one of the first impressions that your customers and clients will have of you. Having a high-quality website with technical functionality are vital essentials that you will need to showcase your brand and who you are as a company.\n<h3><strong>Build a following</strong></h3>\nWebsites and social media pages are one of the first points-of-call for consumers and clients. It contains all the information about you that they will need to know, and all the information that will keep them loyal.\n\nIf you want to get started, this course will give you the best start.\n\nHead over to our <a href=\"https://www.openstudycollege.com/courses/intro-web-design\">website</a> to find out more about the course in detail. Alternatively, give our student advisers a call on <strong>03300 563 100</strong> who will be more than happy to tell you everything you need to know.',NULL,NULL,9,'2018-11-01 11:28:54','2018-11-01 12:09:41',2,'https://blog.openstudycollege.com/?p=8863',1,1,1,0,0,NULL,NULL),
