	(2009,'Courses of the Month - Chartered Management Institute Courses','chartered-management-institute',NULL,NULL,'For many of us, progression and development are vital aspects of our career. In order to do so, we must at some point experience leadership; progression often means more responsibility, including that of people.\n\nTo some, these skills come naturally. To others, it takes some practice and time. But for all, having a qualification in this area of development can benefit us greatly.\n\nWith the job market as competitive as it is, it is important to have skills and qualifications that highlight your abilities and allow you to stand out among the crowd.\n\nIt is because of this that we are highlighting this month?s Course of the Month (or courses, rather). A suite of qualifications from the?\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Chartered Management Institute</strong></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"/storage/images/media_items/old_images/2018/05/leadership-mngt-545783936-002.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-8544\" src=\"/storage/images/media_items/old_images/2018/05/leadership-mngt-545783936.jpg\" height=\"300\" width=\"186\" alt=\"Courses of the Month: CMI Courses\" /></a></p>\n&nbsp;\n\nThe Chartered Management Institute (CMI) is a specialist awarding organisation that offers Management and Leadership, Coaching and Mentoring, and Professional Consulting qualifications.\n\nIt is regulated by four regulators: Ofqual in Englan, CCEA in Northern Ireland, the Qualifications Wales in Wales, and the Scottish Qualification Authority (SQA) in Scotland.\n\nOpen Study College work in partnership with CMI to provide these recognised qualifications through distance learning. The course materials are to the highest standard and we provide high-quality tutor support to assist you through your studies.\n\nWe have launched 9 new courses this month across varying levels to help students who want to develop their career:\n\n<a href=\"https://www.openstudycollege.com/courses/cmi-principles-management-leadership-award-3\"><strong>CMI Level 3 Award in Principles of Management and Leadership</strong></a>\n\n<a href=\"https://www.openstudycollege.com/courses/cmi-principles-management-leadership-certificate-3\"><strong>CMI Level 3 Certificate in Principles of Management and Leadership</strong></a>\n\n<a href=\"https://www.openstudycollege.com/courses/cmi-principles-management-leadership-diploma-3\"><strong>CMI Level 3 Diploma in Principles of Management and Leadership</strong></a>\n\nThe level 3 qualifications are aimed towards aspiring managers or those who are currently in an entry leading position, i.e. team leader or supervisor.\n\n<a href=\"https://www.openstudycollege.com/courses/cmi-management-leadership-award-4\"><strong>CMI Level 4 Award in Management and Leadership</strong></a>\n\n<a href=\"https://www.openstudycollege.com/courses/cmi-management-leadership-certificate-4\"><strong>CMI Level 4 Certificate in Management and Leadership</strong></a>\n\n<a href=\"https://www.openstudycollege.com/courses/cmi-management-leadership-diploma-4\"><strong>CMI Level 4 Diploma in Management and Leadership</strong></a>\n\nAimed towards junior managers, these level 4 qualifications provide the broader skills to be an effective manager with specific leadership skills within your workplace.\n\n<a href=\"https://www.openstudycollege.com/courses/cmi-management-leadership-award-5\"><strong>CMI Level 5 Award in Management and Leadership</strong></a>\n\n<a href=\"https://www.openstudycollege.com/courses/cmi-management-leadership-certificate-5\"><strong>CMI Level 5 Certificate in Management and Leadership</strong></a>\n\n<a href=\"https://www.openstudycollege.com/courses/cmi-management-leadership-diploma-5\"><strong>CMI Level 5 Diploma in Management and Leadership</strong></a>\n\nFor those who have already developed a thriving career, these level 5 courses are designed to provide leadership and performance knowledge for those wanting to become operational, divisional, departmental, regional or specialist managers.\n\nIf one of your New Year\'s Resolutions is to move forward with your career, these courses are a great way to start.\n\nHead over to our <a href=\"https://www.openstudycollege.com/how-it-works\"><strong>website</strong></a> to find out more about these courses or call our student adviser team on <strong>03300 563 100</strong> to discuss your options and enrol today!',NULL,NULL,9,'2019-01-04 11:34:51','2019-02-04 12:26:50',2,'https://blog.openstudycollege.com/?p=8922',1,1,1,0,0,NULL,NULL),
